bilingual.source: The jacket is not too long or too large.
bilingual.target: 这件夹克不太长也不太大。

bilingual.source: They are too short and the nights are too long.

list.abstract: too（英 [tuː]，美 [tuː]），英语单词，副词，意思为太；过于；过度。短语搭配有too much（太多）。例句为“Mopping robots are popular with people who are too busy to do housework.（扫地机很受那些太忙而无法做家务的人的欢迎。）” too相关近义词有greatly、quite等。
TOO，韩国男子演唱组合。 2020年4月1日，发行专辑《REASON FOR BEING :仁》。

yingyinNormal.en: Either they're too old, or they're too young.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不是太老，就是太小。

yingyinNormal.en: Too little, too late, Benji.
yingyinNormal.zh: 太少了，太迟了，Benji！

yingyinNormal.en: Well, maybe we could... Ah-ha. Too slow. Ah-ha. Too cocky.
yingyinNormal.zh: 或许我们可以…你动作太慢了。你太自大了。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, too bad on you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真是太惨了吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Look, I took it too far.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哎呀，我又扯太远了。

yingyinNormal.en: We can too! We just don't much. It's considered rude.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然能！只是不太那么做，那样太粗鲁。

yingyinNormal.en: Our expectations are too low.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们的期望值太低了。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《Facebook COO谢丽尔·桑德伯格哈佛演讲》

yingyinNormal.en: Dry-cleaning? If it's too much... If it's too late...
yingyinNormal.zh: 干洗？如果要求过分了点，又或者时间太晚...

yingyinNormal.en: You're too late. It's gone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你来得太晚了。都结束了。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll kiss your staff. Too late.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我亲吻权杖。太晚了。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb》

yingyinNormal.en: Too many jokes. Must mock Joey.
yingyinNormal.zh: 太滑稽了，快取笑乔伊。

yingyinNormal.en: You're too ambitious for your own good.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你真是野心太大了。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, I'm so happy. Then I'm happy too.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我太高兴了。我也高兴。

yingyinNormal.en: This doesn't look too good, Patrick.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看上去不太妙啊，派崔克。

yingyinNormal.en: This is too much to handle on an empty stomach.
yingyinNormal.zh: 太难以置信了。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, maybe that was just a bit too high.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢，也许那个有一点太高了。

yingyinNormal.en: You don't like ice cream? It's too cold.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不喜欢冰淇淋？它太冰了。

yingyinNormal.en: The states won't go for this. Too radical.
yingyinNormal.zh: 各州不会支持的，太激进了。

yingyinNormal.en: We found them flying too close to humans.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们发现他们飞得离人类太近。

yingyinNormal.en: Nobody wants Rileytown! It's too lollipop!
yingyinNormal.zh: 没人想要去莱丽镇！太幼稚了！

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: They stay in front of screens for <highlight>too</highlight> long.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们在屏幕前待的时间太长了。

examination_example.sentence: It's affordable, and it's got a fun atmosphere without being <highlight>too</highlight> noisy.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它价格合理，气氛有趣，又不太吵闹。

examination_example.sentence: I was beginning to get angry, <highlight>too</highlight>.
When Mrs. Meredith heard of John's idea, she thought it was a good one, <highlight>too</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Meredith太太听到John的想法后，也觉得这是个好主意。

word_usage.usage:
too...to结构在两种情况下不表示否定意义：
①前有not或never修饰或不定式前有not修饰：
One is never too old to learn. 
活到老，学到老。
②too相当于very，常用but、only、all修饰，这时不定式一般表示原因：
I'm only too glad to see you. 
见到你我太高兴了。

数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: And many of your clothes are <highlight>too</highlight> small to wear.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 而且你的很多衣服都太小了，穿不了。

examination_example.sentence: "That kind of dog is <highlight>too</highlight> expensive," said Mama.
Perhaps you are <highlight>too</highlight> busy with your schoolwork to seriously consider these chances.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 也许你太忙于你的学业，没有时间认真考虑这些机会。

examination_example.sentence: She wanted a turn on the swing, <highlight>too</highlight>!
Their sense of smell is well-developed, <highlight>too</highlight>.
Your choice of words can make a big difference, <highlight>too</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你的用词也会有很大的不同。

word_usage.usage:
too...to do sth表示“太……以至于不能做某事”，too后跟形容词或副词，to后跟动词原形。该结构可以转化为so…that引导的结果状语从句。
如：The car is too expensive for me to afford.这辆汽车太贵了，我买不起。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 常用于口语中，语气较轻，通常用于肯定句的句末，too之前通常用逗号和前句分开。
比too和as well正式，一般也不用于否定句，它在句中的位置通常是紧靠动词，即放在行为动词之前，情态动词、助动词或be动词之后。
通常只用于否定句，且要放在句末
多用在口语中，位于肯定句句末，其前不必加逗号。
